description: The Blank is a fictional character that appears in comic books published by Marvel Comics. The character first appears in West Coast Avengers #2 (October 1984) and was created by Roger Stern and Bob Hall.
name: Blank
powers: Wears a personal force field which can protect him from most harm
allows him to slip through the grips of others
anything he held in his hands "blurry," making him impossible to identify.
